quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,31,"Ni jichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo kwa ŵaoga (wakun’jogopa Allah), ngasijiŵa pakutalichila."
  50,32,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Ayi ni yamwapedwaga chilanga, ya jwalijose jwakuujilaujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba), jwakusunga (malamusi Gakwe).”"
  50,33,"“Juŵan’jogwepe Allah mwangali kum’bona, ni jwaiche ni ntima wagalauchila (Kukwakwe pakutenda toba).”"
  51,25,"Pa ndema jaŵajinjile kukwakwe ni ŵatite: “Ntendele!” Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ntendele!” (Ni jwatite soni chamuntima: “Jenumanja ni) ŵandu ŵangamanyika (kukwangu).”"
  51,26,"Ni ŵagalauchile ku ŵapeŵasa ŵakwe (mwangalolechela), ni ŵayiche nako kan’gombe kakunakana (kejoche)."
  51,27,"Ni jwakaŵandichisye kukwao. (Pajwagaweni magasa gao kuti ngagakujigala kulya) jwatite: “Ana uli ngankulya?”"
  52,16,"“Ujinjilani (ni kupasya kupoteka kwakwe), pililani kapena nkapilila yalumope kukwenu, chisimu nkulipidwa yamwaliji nkupanganya.”"
  52,17,"Chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo, ni chindimba."
  52,18,"Achiyisengwelaga yaŵapele M’mbuje gwao (Allah), aku M’mbuje gwao ali ŵagosile ku ilagasyo ya Moto Waukali."
  53,10,"Basi (Allah) ni jwaajuuwiile kwa kapolo Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ya jwaajuuwiile (kupitila mwa Jibulilu)."
  53,11,"Ntima (wa Muhammadi ﷺ) nganiulambusya pa yajwaiweni (ni meso gakwe)."
  53,12,"Ana ni nkukangana najo pa yajukuiona?"
  54,1,"Ndaŵi (jakwichila Kiyama) jiŵandichile, ni ugaanjiiche mwesi. ",footnotes:1:Akusimulila Anas رضى الله عنه yanti: “Ŵandu ŵa pa Maaka ŵam’bendile Ntenga jwa Allahﷺkuti jwalosye chisimosimo, basi ni jwalosisye ganjika kwa mwesi.” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 3438).
  54,2,"Soni naga ali achiweni chisimosimo akasanyosyaga, ni akutiji: “(Awu ni) usaŵi wakwendelechela.”"
  54,3,"Ni ŵaakaaniile, ni kuya isako yao, sano chindu chilichose (chambone kapena chakusakala chaŵapanganyisye mundu) chiŵele chakutamilichika (malipilo gakwe lisiku lya Kiyama)."